00406         public:
00408             const bool Sort(
00409                     const int (*cmp)(const T&, const T&)    
00410 
00411                     )
00412             {
00413                 bool b_Result = true;
00414                 if (GetCount() < 2)
00415                 {
00416                     b_Result = true;
00417                 }
00418                 else
00419                 {
00420                     // Get a reference element.
00421                     T t_Ref = RemoveTail();
00422 
00423                     // Dispatch elements in q_1 and q_2.
00424                     Queue<T> q_1(0), q_2(0);
00425                     while (! IsEmpty())
00426                     {
00427                         T t_Sort = RemoveTail();
00428                         if (cmp(t_Sort, t_Ref) > 0)
00429                         {
00430                             q_1.AddTail(t_Sort);
00431                         }
00432                         else
00433                         {
00434                             q_2.AddTail(t_Sort);
00435                         }
00436                     }
00437 
00438                     // Sort each list q_1 and q_2
00439                     if (q_1.Sort(cmp) && q_2.Sort(cmp))
00440                     {
00441                         // Eventually restore q_1...
00442                         b_Result = true;
00443                         for (   Iterator it_1 = q_1.GetIterator();
00444                                 q_1.IsValid(it_1);
00445                                 q_1.MoveNext(it_1))
00446                         {
00447                             if (! AddTail(q_1.GetAt(it_1)))
00448                             {
00449                                 b_Result = false;
00450                             }
00451                         }
00452                         // ... then the reference element...
00453                         if (! AddTail(t_Ref))
00454                         {
00455                             b_Result = false;
00456                         }
00457                         // ... and then q_2.
00458                         for (   Iterator it_2 = q_2.GetIterator();
00459                                 q_2.IsValid(it_2);
00460                                 q_2.MoveNext(it_2))
00461                         {
00462                             if (! AddTail(q_2.GetAt(it_2)))
00463                             {
00464                                 b_Result = false;
00465                             }
00466                         }
00467                     }
00468                 }
00469                 return b_Result;
00470             }
